sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Angular
    participant GW as Gateway YARP
    participant BE as Writer BE
    participant RC as rag_client
    participant RAG as rag-service

    FE->>GW: POST multipart file and conversation_id with Bearer JWT
    GW->>BE: forwards request
    BE->>BE: require_user returns 401 if no token
    BE->>RC: upload_document user_id conv_id bytes
    RC->>RC: mint internal JWT with conv_id claim
    RC->>RAG: POST multipart with Bearer
    RAG->>RAG: parse and chunk and embed and store
    RAG-->>RC: document_id status chunk_count
    RC-->>BE: dict
    BE-->>FE: 201 with document_id status chunk_count
